{"id": 2407, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得在亲密关系里，人们怎么表示才算真正的“我愿意”？", "description": "在你看来，如何能够更好地沟通和表达性关系中的“同意”？（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 279, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180610172816xWKDylVB5SEoCbMm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 286465, "content": "看到他有冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371086}, {"id": 286466, "content": "那你来啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 286467, "content": "楼下邀请上去做客，牵手不闪躲，接下来不推开。一条单身?的看法", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591076}, {"id": 286471, "content": "来，把拳头伸进去吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143591}, {"id": 286472, "content": "综合经验来看只要愿意和你去开房，就表示已经同意亲密关系的确定了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 286473, "content": "对不起，没感受过", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357764}, {"id": 286474, "content": "一口含住", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370345}, {"id": 286475, "content": "对视", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374987}, {"id": 286478, "content": "可以共同使用一个杯子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217703}, {"id": 286479, "content": "喝同一杯饮料吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705412}, {"id": 286480, "content": "主动分享自己的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341854}, {"id": 286405, "content": "主动发出“要不要到我家坐坐喝点东西”的邀请", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 286406, "content": "在做出试探时不躲闪抗拒", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 286407, "content": "直接说出肯定的答复，而